00:13:33.277 --> 00:13:35.356
Pojdite tja.

00:13:36.529 --> 00:13:38.529
Vzemite sinov pepel

00:13:39.365 --> 00:13:41.615
in ga potresite
po stopnicah svetišča.

00:13:42.286 --> 00:13:43.865
Zaprite se noter

00:13:44.328 --> 00:13:46.369
in ko pride noč,

00:13:46.874 --> 00:13:48.463
bo prišel k vam.

00:13:50.126 --> 00:13:53.667
Lahko se boste pogovarjali
z njim skozi vrata svetišča,

00:13:54.505 --> 00:13:56.165
se dokončno poslovili.

00:14:02.514 --> 00:14:05.024
