Mažejo se s pepelom

00:18:34.787 --> 00:18:36.997
in se hranijo
z mesom umrlih.

00:18:39.165 --> 00:18:42.996
Verjamejo, da jim to pomaga
pri komuniciranju z drugo stranjo.

00:19:09.320 --> 00:19:12.320
