nato sledite mojim navodilom.

00:19:12.365 --> 00:19:14.328
Joj, Michael.
–Dala mu bom sporočilo.

00:19:14.367 --> 00:19:16.488
Ves iz sebe bo
in Lucy mora vedeti, kje sem.

00:19:16.537 --> 00:19:18.537
Poskrbela bom za vse.

00:19:49.944 --> 00:19:53.025
