00:52:15.014 --> 00:52:16.974
Bel šal imam.
To ni dovolj?

00:52:17.016 --> 00:52:18.317
Ne.

00:52:18.518 --> 00:52:21.349
Oprosti, nisem hotela
biti nevljudna do Chila in Billa.

00:52:22.356 --> 00:52:24.356
Tu je dober kraj.

00:52:31.239 --> 00:52:33.699
Adijo, Chil. Adijo, Bill.

00:52:39.998 --> 00:52:41.998
