01:19:53.923 --> 01:19:56.514
Kaj? Zakaj?

01:19:58.220 --> 01:19:59.890
Ker se je Oliver vrnil.

01:20:03.434 --> 01:20:04.644
Kaj?

01:20:04.893 --> 01:20:07.273
Oliver se je vrnil
in mislim, da je ubil Piki.

01:20:07.311 --> 01:20:10.112
Ker je hotela sežgati njegove
reči in ga poslati nazaj.

01:20:10.149 --> 01:20:11.609
Ker ni več najin sin.

01:20:11.649 --> 01:20:12.939
Nehaj.

01:20:14.153 --> 01:20:15.363
Draga, nehaj.

01:20:15.404 --> 01:20:17.243
Vem, da zveni čisto noro,
toda res je.

01:20:17.698 --> 01:20:19.408
Kajne, Luce? Kajne?

01:20:20.868 --> 01:20:23.497
Ne vem, kaj govoriš, mami.

01:20:23.787 --> 01:20:26.207
Ne, srček, je že v redu.

01:20:26.247 --> 01:20:27.618
Zdaj lahko poveva očku.

01:20:27.666 --> 01:20:29.666
Povej o bratu.
Povej o klavirju.

01:20:29.710 --> 01:20:31.340
Povej mu o klavirju.

01:20:32.337 --> 01:20:35.587
Ne vem, kaj hočeš reči.
Oliver je mrtev.

01:20:36.507 --> 01:20:39.137
Luce, ne vem,
zakaj zdaj to delaš.

01:20:39.177 --> 01:20:41.097
Ampak moraš očetu
povedati resnico.

01:20:41.137 --> 01:20:42.557
Moraš mu povedati.

01:20:43.015 --> 01:20:46.057
Ne vem, kaj misliš, mami.
–Lucy, moraš mu povedati!

01:20:46.100 --> 01:20:48.140
Dovolj! Dovolj!

01:20:49.729 --> 01:20:51.399
Strašiš jo.

01:20:52.565 --> 01:20:55.395
Oprosti. Žal mi je, ampak …

01:21:01.408 --> 01:21:02.698
Je že v redu.

01:21:02.743 --> 01:21:04.792
Nesel te bom
v posteljo, srček.

01:21:05.828 --> 01:21:06.998
V redu.

01:21:09.625 --> 01:21:11.175
Se počutiš bolje?

01:21:11.502 --> 01:21:13.171
Zdaj ko si ti tu, očka.

01:21:16.756 --> 01:21:19.127
Lepo spi, prav.
Rad te imam.

01:21:19.176 --> 01:21:20.386
Jaz tudi tebe.

01:21:20.426 --> 01:21:22.256
Lucy, prosim,
povej očku o Oliverju.

01:21:23.514 --> 01:21:25.724
Maria, ljubica, zmedena si.

01:21:25.765 --> 01:21:27.426
Pogovoriva se spodaj.
–Ne izmišljujem si.

01:21:27.475 --> 01:21:30.595
Vem, da misliš,
da si ne izmišljuješ, ampak …

01:21:33.689 --> 01:21:34.819
Kaj?

01:21:38.112 --> 01:21:39.702
Oliver, kaj si naredil?

01:21:45.034 --> 01:21:47.500
Maria?
–Obsedel jo je.

01:21:47.537 --> 01:21:49.078
Maria, kaj govoriš?

01:21:49.122 --> 01:21:50.372
Ne, ne!

01:21:51.457 --> 01:21:52.667
Oliver?

01:21:54.711 --> 01:21:55.881
Maria.

01:21:56.171 --> 01:21:58.341
Lahko sva spet skupaj.

01:21:58.381 --> 01:21:59.971
Pusti sestro pri miru!

01:22:00.007 --> 01:22:01.427
Očka, bojim se!

01:22:01.467 --> 01:22:02.797
Nehaj!

01:22:07.682 --> 01:22:08.932
Pridi sem, ljubica.

01:22:08.975 --> 01:22:10.345
Vse bo v redu.

01:22:10.394 --> 01:22:11.694
Michael.

01:22:12.813 --> 01:22:14.023
Pomoč potrebuješ.

01:22:14.064 --> 01:22:16.524
Priskrbel ti bom pomoč
in vse bo v redu.

01:22:22.823 --> 01:22:25.372
Dobro.
Je vse v redu, srček?

01:22:25.408 --> 01:22:26.698
Mami me je tepla.

01:22:26.743 --> 01:22:29.003
Ne, mami zdaj ni pri sebi.

01:22:29.037 --> 01:22:30.867
Ampak zelo te ima rada.

01:22:31.247 --> 01:22:32.667
In jaz tudi.

01:22:33.751 --> 01:22:35.171
Kam pa greva?

01:22:35.210 --> 01:22:37.050
Na majhno pustolovščino.

01:22:49.515 --> 01:22:50.676
Kaj hočete?

01:23:03.279 --> 01:23:04.579
Dobro.

01:23:07.743 --> 01:23:09.582
Ostani tu,
na hitro bom nekam poklical.

01:23:10.871 --> 01:23:12.541
Vse bo v redu.

01:23:14.041 --> 01:23:15.081
Dobro.

01:23:15.375 --> 01:23:16.454
Dajmo.

01:23:18.628 --> 01:23:19.748
Dajmo.

01:23:40.067 --> 01:23:41.146
Halo. Dober dan.

01:23:43.569 --> 01:23:49.619
Moj naslov je Dobra Villa 17,
Carter Road v Bandri.

01:23:49.952 --> 01:23:52.702
Pred mojo hišo
je skupina moških.

01:23:52.746 --> 01:23:55.416
Mislim, da hočejo vdreti
in vzeti mojo hčer.

01:23:55.998 --> 01:23:57.328
Ne vem,
toda takoj potrebujem pomoč.

01:23:58.752 --> 01:23:59.921
Poreden pes.

01:24:00.753 --> 01:24:01.923
Ja. Ja.

01:24:02.256 --> 01:24:03.626
Čim hitreje.

01:24:05.134 --> 01:24:06.384
Tiho.

01:24:06.426 --> 01:24:09.096
Ne vem,
ampak skoraj goli so.

01:24:09.137 --> 01:24:10.637
Prosim, pohitite. Ja.

01:24:14.768 --> 01:24:16.268
Lucy, kaj …

01:24:19.689 --> 01:24:21.359
O mojbog, srček.

01:24:23.359 --> 01:24:24.489
Kaj si naredila?

01:24:25.612 --> 01:24:27.412
Winston je bil poreden.

01:24:27.448 --> 01:24:29.278
Morala sem ga kaznovati.

01:24:31.659 --> 01:24:33.250
Saj ne boš še ti poreden,

01:24:33.287 --> 01:24:34.957
kaj, očka?

01:24:36.038 --> 01:24:37.189
Ne!

01:24:38.041 --> 01:24:40.291
Zdaj sva sama z mamico.

01:24:50.136 --> 01:24:51.256
Žal mi je, oči.

01:24:51.305 --> 01:24:53.475
Nisem te hotela raniti.

01:24:57.351 --> 01:24:59.811
Vsa kuhinjska tla boš umazal.

01:24:59.854 --> 01:25:01.614
Mami bo jezna.

01:25:02.649 --> 01:25:05.109
Lucy, kaj delaš?

01:25:05.610 --> 01:25:07.490
Nisem Lucy, Oliver sem.

01:25:08.363 --> 01:25:09.823
Ne.

01:25:10.157 --> 01:25:11.657
Pa sem!

01:25:44.983 --> 01:25:46.073
Michael?

01:26:13.679 --> 01:26:14.719
Michael.

01:26:24.230 --> 01:26:25.360
Michael?

01:26:41.957 --> 01:26:43.247
Oliver!

01:26:50.757 --> 01:26:52.627
Pomagaj mi, mami!

01:26:52.926 --> 01:26:54.216
Pusti jo!

01:26:57.972 --> 01:26:59.063
Lucy!

01:26:59.099 --> 01:27:00.389
Mami.
–Lucy!

01:27:00.434 --> 01:27:01.634
Srček!

01:27:02.935 --> 01:27:04.136
Luce!

01:27:11.653 --> 01:27:12.853
Lucy!

01:27:43.519 --> 01:27:44.849
Ne!

01:27:47.939 --> 01:27:49.189
Lucy!

01:27:50.359 --> 01:27:51.578
Ne!

01:27:54.863 --> 01:27:57.283
Oliver, pusti Lucy
in pridi k meni.

01:27:57.865 --> 01:27:59.826
Pridi k meni, slišiš?

01:27:59.868 --> 01:28:01.118
Nočem iti nazaj.

01:28:01.161 --> 01:28:03.501
Vem, vem,
ampak jaz bom šla s tabo.

01:28:04.163 --> 01:28:05.173
Prav?

01:28:09.293 --> 01:28:14.304
Ne bo ti hudega.
Na varnem si. Imam te, imam te.

01:28:25.476 --> 01:28:27.146
Vzemite raje mene.

01:28:28.188 --> 01:28:29.358
Ne!

01:28:32.024 --> 01:28:33.734
Ne! Ne!

01:28:34.194 --> 01:28:35.203
Maria!

01:28:36.697 --> 01:28:37.987
Ne!

01:28:38.865 --> 01:28:40.195
Pustite me!

01:30:09.622 --> 01:30:10.672
Ne!

01:30:19.841 --> 01:30:21.301
Mami!

01:30:35.815 --> 01:30:36.855
Maria?

01:30:39.319 --> 01:30:40.609
Michael?

01:30:40.654 --> 01:30:42.783
Maria, me slišiš?

01:30:43.657 --> 01:30:45.287
Michael, kje si?

01:30:45.701 --> 01:30:47.291
Tukaj sem, ljubica.

01:30:48.453 --> 01:30:50.123
Ne morem verjeti,
da slišim tvoj glas.

01:30:51.457 --> 01:30:52.537
Ljubica?

01:30:54.208 --> 01:30:55.408
Maria?

01:30:57.880 --> 01:30:59.130
Me slišiš?

01:31:00.841 --> 01:31:02.970
Draga, prosim,
moram te videti.

01:31:03.010 --> 01:31:04.470
Michael?
–Prosim, kje si?

01:31:04.511 --> 01:31:06.470
Ne.
–Ljubica, me slišiš?

01:31:06.512 --> 01:31:08.774
Ne. –Moram te videti.
–Michael.

01:31:08.806 --> 01:31:10.981
Moram videti tvoj obraz.
–Ne!

01:31:11.476 --> 01:31:12.617
Ne!

